question: Will OpenAI Merge with Anthropic in 2023?
description:
This market will resolve to "Yes" if is officially announced that OpenAI and Anthropic have agreed to merge by Dec 31, 2023, 11:59 PM ET.

The announcement must indicate that the two organizations have agreed to combine their operations. This could be a legal merger where they form one entity, a joint venture, or an acquisition of one by the other.

If no such announcement is made by Dec 31, the market will resolve to "No". Note that an announcement before the end date of a OpenAI/Anthropic merger will suffice to resolve this market to "Yes" regardless of if or when the merger actually occurs.

The resolution source will be official statements from OpenAI and/or Anthropic, however a consensus of credible reporting will also be used.

question: Will CZ remain CEO of Binance through 2023?
description:
This market will resolve to "Yes" if Changpeng Zhao (CZ) remains CEO of Binance from the date of this market's inception, November 21, through December 31, 2023, 11:59 PM ET. Otherwise, this market will resolve to "No".

An announcement that CZ will no longer be CEO on or before December 31 will not be sufficient to resolve this market. Only confirmation that CZ is no longer CEO of Binance within the market timeframe will result in this market resolving to "No".

This market's primary resolution source will be official information from Binance and/or CZ, however a consensus of credible reporting sources will also be used.
